{"tid":2202764,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：當今第一戰神走入戰場。","createTime":"2020-09-15T00:00:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-15T01:55:00.000Z","uid":271829,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"af9206afd75c8a5eae1bccb3eaea385a6164dda3","tid":2202764,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T00:00:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C6QbcWk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC6QbcWk.jpg&h=c1fe42bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n陳雲：國師錦囊。當今世上第一戰神，解釋是日金句。<br />\n冷戰愈和平。結果愈凶險。<br />\n對中國如是，對香港更是。前蘇聯是和平應對冷戰，結果呢？四分五裂，慘不忍睹。戰場的地獄，是為膽怯者準備的。<br />\n中共肯定會墮入戰場的地獄，被和平的機器絞殺。<br />\n（圖：當今第一戰神走入戰場。）"},{"pid":"4a5c3e6fa2bb254551eb773f95efe77f6085c833","tid":2202764,"uid":84128,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T00:01:58.000Z","msg":"敵將 是doctor lee"},{"pid":"9ac4a8eaf8bef180f0e9316c33004027c53453e7","tid":2202764,"uid":4493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T00:02:44.000Z","msg":"係唔係希爾頓 佢屋企樓下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13e670c8f7d968c4b582fa281972b766c184d3b7","tid":2202764,"uid":108225,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9ac4a8eaf8bef180f0e9316c33004027c53453e7","tid":2202764,"uid":4493,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T00:02:44.000Z","msg":"係唔係希爾頓 佢屋企樓下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T00:04:13.000Z","msg":"係戰場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你唔識野"},{"pid":"0e6922a131c4bbfa343c086286dd7ffb5a9053cf","tid":2202764,"uid":48631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-15T00:04:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wiki.komica.org/images/5/51/Img831.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.komica.org%2Fimages%2F5%2F51%2FImg831.jpg&h=9d478183&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eea38c64f9dd77fea41